:

1. *Verovao* sam u njega, ali on me je izdao. (I trusted him, but he betrayed me.)
2. Ona je *verovala* da će sve biti u redu. (She believed that everything would be okay.)
3. Oni su *verovali* da će im sve uspeti. (They believed that they would succeed in everything.)
4. Nisam *verovao* u tvoje obećanje. (I didn't believe in your promise.)
5. Njegovi prijatelji su mu *verovali*. (His friends trusted him.)